GTW To-Do
=========

- GTW.NAV.Robots: Answer to url `/robots.txt`

  * Disallow for various directories/pages
    (NAV.E_Type, NAV.Sitemap, NAV.Auth, ...)

  * http://www.robotstxt.org/robotstxt.html

- GTW.NAV.E_Type.Admin

  * Introduce E_Type_Admin_Desc and E_Type_Admin_Group_Desc

    + reify the information contained in GTW.OMP.XXX.Nav.Admin

    + allow grouping of E_Type specific Admin pages under a Admin Group

    + allow `admin_args` argument to `GTW.NAV.E_Type.Manager` to refer to a
      `E_Type_Admin_Group_Desc` (doesn't need the name of the `E_Type`; DRY!)

    + Change GTW.NAV.Site_Admin

      - to include etypes from `top.E_Types` only if they aren't explicitly
        specified

      - must allow multiple E_Types to map to the same GTW.NAV.E_Type.Manager
        instance (i.e., Site_Admin needs to iterate over the keys of
        `top.E_Types`, not over its values!)

